{
  "message": "\u2728 Redesign Demo Install Guide as banner + modal (#251)\n\nReplace the floating card with a purple gradient banner positioned\ndirectly under the demo mode banner. Clicking \"Install Guide\" opens\na modal with clear 1-2-3 steps:\n  1. brew install kubestellar/tap/kc (backend + frontend + agent)\n  2. kc (starts everything)\n  3. Configure AI keys in Settings\n\nThe banner is dismissible with localStorage persistence. The modal\nincludes copy-to-clipboard commands, a Settings link, docs link,\nExit Demo button, and a \"Got it\" close button.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>\nCo-authored-by: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
